extendedInfo.description: Hello repair unit11010, the main memory unit has crashed and must be repaired. As BOT time and battery power areagainst you as you traverse intelligently designed mazes and collect puzzle pieces to regain your memory and try torestore power to the core of the system, the CUBE. As long as the core exists so shall you. Discover BOTs story andunravel the secrets of the CUBE. Collect special abilities that allow BOT to overcome his virtual prison. Are you CUBED?
